# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
"""
Created on Thu Mar  7 22:02:10 2019

@author: Blake

While the dataCollection program can work on all games, this analysis program cannot.
This analysis program is specific to Rust. It will work on Rust data from the Steam Market but it will not work with other games.
For example, a lot of the data cleaning is to catagorize specific skins for specific items in Rust. CSGO does not 
have an eoka pistol and as such you may get errors. 

I hope you will use this code to help you in analyzing your own data for your own purposes by using my methods and formats for data
cleaning, organizing, and analysis. I do not encourage you to just copy and paste this code as 1) it only works for Rust
and 2) it is specific to my questions.

"""
